    "122356773": {
      "title": "The mass gap for the P (\u03c6) 2 quantum field model with a strong external field",
      "abstract": "We consider theP(\u03c6)2 hamiltonian whose interaction density is given by ::: ::: $$\\lambda P(\\phi (x)) + \\mu \\phi (x)^k $$ ::: ::: wherek is odd and 1\u2266k<degP. For sufficiently large \u03bc we show that there is a gap in the energy spectrum. In addition we obtain new regions of analyticity in \u03bb and \u03bc for the Schwinger functions and the pressure."
